        HEY_YOU_RE_IN_THE_WAY_WE_FORTIFYIN                                    = 7426,  -- Hey, you're in the way. We fortifyin' this here wall to withstand the beastmen's siege turrets. So how's about just gettin' outta here before you get hurt.
