        THAT_OLD_COOT_OF_AN_ELVAAN_WITH_THE                                   = 7436,  -- That old coot of an Elvaan with the huge axe strapped across his back is a carpenter. Famous 'round these parts. Make sure you get him workin' with earth crystals.
        MAY_NOT_LOOK_IT_BUT_THE_MITHRA_WITH                                   = 7437,  -- May not look it, but the Mithra with the black kerchief wrapped 'round her noggin is an architect. She's gonna need her lightning crystals.
        THAT_SPRAT_OF_A_TARUTARU_WEARIN_THE_BLUE                              = 7438,  -- That sprat of a Tarutaru wearin' the blue getup's a handy lil' plumber. Surin' he'll be wantin' his water crystals, no doubt.
        THE_GOOD_LOOKING_FELLA_IN_ALL_WHITE_DOES                              = 7439,  -- The good-looking fella in all white does scaffoldin'. Young Hume lad. See to it he's usin' light crystals.
        THE_LADY_ELVAAN_S_A_PAINTER_HANDLES_A                                 = 7440,  -- The lady Elvaan's a painter. Handles a brush like nobody I never seen. Need dark crystals in that line of work. And that's it.
        AHHH_ONE_MORE_THING_IF_YOU_RE_TOO                                     = 7441,  -- Ahhh, one more thing. If you're too late issuin' your orders, they're liable to up and leave their posts. So be right, and be quick.
