        SINCE_TIME_IMMEMORIAL_ELDERLY_ELVAAN_HAVE_COME_HERE                   = 7735,  -- Since time immemorial, elderly Elvaan have come here to await their final rest. Many pilgrims of other races, too, have ended their journeys here, wishing to be close to the Nurturer.
        OF_COURSE_FAITH_AND_DISCIPLINE_ARE_VIRTUES_BUT                        = 7736,  -- Of course, faith and discipline are virtues. But life is to be enjoyed, and the lives of others respected. Faith can wait until these two things are accomplished.
        I_TOLD_THIS_TO_A_GALKA_FRIEND_AND                                     = 7737,  -- I told this to a Galka friend, and he bellowed a hearty laugh. Yet I could see his point: those who only live a short while have no time for such thoughts.
