        I_GUESS_YOU_RE_RIGHT_HERE_TAKE_YOUR                                   = 7774,  -- I guess you're right. Here, take your shiny new map...
        Y_YOU_VE_ALREADY_GOT_ONE_WELL_THEN                                    = 7775,  -- Y-you've already got one? Well, then I'll just have to think of something else to recompense you for your troubles. Then how about...h-hey! Wait! That's mine...!
        I_GUESS_I_SHOULD_BE_HAPPY_TO_HAVE                                     = 7776,  -- I guess I should be happy to have this old, tattered map back. No, really, I'm grateful...
