        I_DON_T_HAVE_TIME_TO_ENTERTAIN_THE                                    = 7799,  -- I don't have time to entertain the likes of you. Get out of my face.
        SO_YOU_RE_FROM_WHAT_IS_THAT_TO                                        = 7800,  -- So you're from [San d'Oria/Bastok/Windurst]. What is that to me? I have no interest in your battles. I go where I want, when I want. No one can take that from me. Not you, not some [king/president/sibyl], not anyone.
        HOLD_ON_YOU_HAVEN_T_HAPPENED_TO_HEAR                                  = 7801,  -- Hold on... You haven't happened to hear anything about an Ensetsu, have you? His family's supposed to be living somewhere in Bastok.
        AH_NEVER_MIND_FORGET_YOU_HEARD_ANYTHING_FROM                          = 7802,  -- Ah, never mind. Forget you heard anything from me.
        WHAT_THE_HELL_IS_THIS_DO_I_LOOK                                       = 7803,  -- What the hell is this? Do I look like a goldsmith? Get that thing out of my face!
        HAH_YOU_THINK_YOU_CAN_BUY_MY_LOYALTY                                  = 7804,  -- Hah! You think you can buy my loyalty with a single throwing star!?
        HMPH_I_MIGHT_CONSIDER_HELPING_OUT_BUT_I                               = 7805,  -- Hmph... I might consider helping out [your kingdom/your republic/your federation], but I won't be making you any promises.
        I_SENSE_SOMETHING_OTHERWORLDLY_ABOUT_YOU_TRAVELER_BUT                 = 7806,  -- I sense something...otherworldly about you, traveler. But appearances can oft be misleading, nay?
        IT_MAY_HAP_THE_SECRETS_I_SEEK_LIE                                     = 7807,  -- It may hap the secrets I seek lie with [the Crimson Lion/the Republic/the Federation]...
        AH_SO_YOUR_NATION_REQUESTS_MY_SERVICES_I                              = 7808,  -- Ah, so your nation requests my services... I shall consider your proposal...
        I_HAVE_HEARD_RUMOR_THAT_THE_LORD_OF                                   = 7809,  -- I have heard rumor that the lord of the beastmen sits upon an hoary throne in the frozen north. Do you believe he would entertain a raven?
        I_AM_OFFERING_A_PRAYER_FOR_THOSE_POOR                                 = 7810,  -- I am offering a prayer for those poor souls whose lives have been prematurely extinguished. And you...you are bound for the battlefield, are you not? My thoughts are with you also.
        YOUR_PRESENCE_EVOKES_LONG_FORGOTTEN_MEMORIES_WITHIN_AND               = 7811,  -- Your presence evokes long-forgotten memories within and reminds me of the hopes and dreams that were my driving force in youth. Insignificant though my powers may be, perhaps the time has come to return to the fray and do my part for the greater good.
        YOU_HAVE_MY_GRATITUDE_MAY_YOU_FIND_FAVOR                              = 7812,  -- You have my gratitude. May you find favor with the Goddess.
        LYSANDER_THIS_IS_A_KEY_LOCATION_IN_JEUNO                              = 7813,  -- Lysander! This is a key location in Jeuno's defenses. Don't think you can take it easy when I'm not looking over your shoulder!
        HEH_WHY_DON_T_YOU_GO_AHEAD_AND                                        = 7814,  -- Heh, why don't you go ahead and chase all those beastmen off for me, then?
        HAH_YOU_MAKE_IT_SOUND_A_SIMPLE_TASK                                   = 7815,  -- Hah! You make it sound a simple task! These are the fiends that bathed Windurst in blood, and crushed the Royal Knights of San d'Oria!
        DON_T_WHIMPER_LIKE_A_LITTLE_GIRL_CARLISLE                             = 7816,  -- Don't whimper like a little girl, Carlisle!
        I_HAVE_FAITH_IN_YOUR_AMAZING_LUCK_ON                                  = 7817,  -- I have faith in your amazing luck on the battlefield!
        CAPTAIN_LYSANDER_LOOK_ANOTHER_OF_THOSE_MONSTROSITIES                  = 7818,  -- Captain Lysander! Look! Another of those monstrosities...!
        SO_WE_HAVE_A_MAW_IN_NOW_TOO                                           = 7819,  -- So, we have a maw in [Batallia Downs/the Rolanberry Fields/Sauromugue Champaign] now, too...
        HOW_MANY_OF_THESE_THINGS_DO_WE_HAVE                                   = 7820,  -- How many of these things do we have confirmed?
        WELL_SIR_THERE_S_ONE_IN_ONE_IN                                        = 7821,  -- Well, sir, there's one in [Batallia Downs/the Rolanberry Fields/Sauromugue Champaign], one in [Batallia Downs/the Rolanberry Fields/Sauromugue Champaign], and now this one in [Batallia Downs/the Rolanberry Fields/Sauromugue Champaign]...
        ALYSTAIR_AREN_T_YOU_FORGETTING_THE_REPORTS_FROM                       = 7822,  -- Alystair. Aren't you forgetting the reports from our allies?
        AH_YOU_RE_QUITE_CORRECT_SIR                                           = 7823,  -- Ah, you're quite correct, sir!
        INCLUDING_THE_THREE_JEUNO_HAS_CONFIRMED_THERE_HAVE                    = 7824,  -- Including the three Jeuno has confirmed, there have been nine maws discovered in total, sir.
        HAHAHA_YOU_NEEDN_T_BE_SO_FORMAL_SON                                   = 7825,  -- Hahaha. You needn't be so formal, son. This isn't the parade ground.
        STILL_THAT_S_NOT_A_SMALL_AMOUNT_EVEN                                  = 7826,  -- Still, that's not a small amount, even if they are spread over two continents...
